@no-cookie-jar=false

### Register a new user
POST {{host}}/api/user
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Sebastian Curtis",
  "last_name": "Lavarias",
  "mobile_number": "09972217704",
  "email": "sebastian.lavarias@kislap.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Invalid registration (missing required fields)
POST {{host}}/api/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "",
  "last_name": "",
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "password": ""
}

### Register without mobile number (nullable)
POST {{host}}/api/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Alice",
  "last_name": "Smith",
  "mobile_number": "",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "mypassword"
}
